description:
Danny welcomes back LeeAnne Locken to Everything Iconic to discuss this season of Real Housewives of Dallas, her wedding, and more! Julie & Brandy also pop by to chat gay politics and The People's Couch. Plus, a lil #RHOBH scoop, #RHOC recap, and lots more.


LeeAnne: 12:57

RHOC: 36:10ish

Julie & Brandy: 46:30ish
